      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 featuring the high-strung S54B32 inline-six engine. This unit delivers linear power through its six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. Mechanically, the car is robust: the dual-VANOS system has been recently serviced, and the rear subframe\u2014a known E46 weak point\u2014has been professionally reinforced. The suspension retains its factory-tuned geometry, providing exceptional turn-in and lateral grip via the M-Variable differential lock. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain and chassis remain tight, making this an ideal specimen for the purist who values mechanical pedigree and tactile feedback over a garage-queen status.",
